tool_description: An API generating random pickup lines

api_list.name: Tinder
api_list.description: Get a random tinder pickup line.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://pick-me-up.p.rapidapi.com/tinder"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "pick-me-up.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
